QueueResource.Status Property

Definition

Namespace:
Microsoft.Azure.Management.ServiceBus.Models
Assembly:
Microsoft.Azure.Management.ServiceBus.dll

In this Article

Gets or sets enumerates the possible values for the status of a messaging entity. Possible values include: 'Active', 'Creating', 'Deleting', 'Disabled', 'ReceiveDisabled', 'Renaming', 'Restoring', 'SendDisabled', 'Unknown'

public Nullable<Microsoft.Azure.Management.ServiceBus.Models.EntityStatus> Status { get; set; }
